核心能力 Competence
■ 具電機工程相關領域之專業知識。
 To possess professional knowledge in the field of electrical engineering.
□ 策劃及執行專題研究之能力。
 The ability to plan and carry out a research project.
■ 撰寫專業論文之能力。
 To write a professional-quality dissertation.
■ 創新思考及獨立解決問題之能力。
 Innovative thinking and the ability to solve problems independently.
■ 跨領域人員協調整合之能力。
 Multidisciplinary coordination and integration capabilities.
□ 好的國際觀以及理解專業倫理與社會責任之能力。
 A solid international outlook and the ability to understand professional ethics and social responsibility.
□ 領導、管理及規劃之能力。
 Leadership, management and planning abilities.
□ 終身自我學習成長之能力
 The ability to learn and develop throughout life.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       1 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Mixed-Signal IP (Intellectual Property)中常用的子區塊電路之設計原理及實務教導混合訊號晶片電路模擬所需知識教導類比晶片電路佈局及下線所需知識，幫助同學完成1st-cut work之成品 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction2Mixed-Signal System and IP Examples3Stability of Operational Amplifiers4Systematic Design of Operational Amplifiers5Fully-Differential Amplifiers6Design of Multi-Stage Operational Amplifiers7Rail-to-Rail Input and Output Amplifiers8Class AB and Driver Amplifiers9Midterm Exam.10Switched-Capacitor Filters11Continuous-Time Filters12Voltage Reference Circuits13Low Dropout Regulators (LDOs)14Analog Layout Considerations15I/O Pads and Packages16Coupling Effects in Mixed Analog-Digital ICs17Modeling and Simulation of Analog Circuits using Verilog-AMS18Final Presentation 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


